title: THE MANDALORIAN Episode 5 Breakdown! IS BOBA FETT BACK? New Theories and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: Is Boba Fett back? Or is this a big Jar Jar stepping in a pile of doo doo? Leave me your thoughts below.
Let's be honest, this series is turning out to be 100 times better than the last 5 Star Wars films.
This episode was one big call back to the original and prequel trilogies

*Hit me with your Beskar*

Them intros are getting better and better
There’s another sound when Boba steps into frame after Han and Jabba finish talking in A New Hope. It’s his radar sound, the same that’s in this episode.
